# Security

- Jira token: Supabase Vault only; mask as `****************` in UI/API
- Never log tokens or full `raw_jira_data`
- All routes: authenticated, non-candidate user
- CSRF on all POST endpoints
- Personal data in assignee/reporter fields + raw_jira_data (BB-LIFE-04)
- Inngest webhooks: verify signing key
